        ],
        [
          "Classification",
          "Intelligent Tutoring System",
          "Performance on Next Question",
          "Correct (1) vs Incorrect (0)",
          "4417 ASSISTments09 learners, 19917 ASSISTments15 learners, 686 ASSISTmentsChall learners, 333 Statics learners, 2000 Simulated learners",
          "ASSISTments, Statics",
          "Sequences of Answers",
          "[Concatenated Learner Embeddings]",
          "Sequential models, such as DKT, while effective, often fail to capture longer-term dependencies → the larger the input sequence, the more noisy the model will be.",
          "Authors employ multi-head attention which was shown to be better for modelling longer-term dependencies in sequences. \n\nHowever, the problem of attention is that the sequential information is somewhat lost, which is the reason why the authors propose KTA-LSTM.",
          "Authors do dataset specific models. Weight initialization comes from Xavier iniatialization.",
          "BKT, PFA, DKT, DKT+, KTA, KTA_LSTM, SAKT, AKT, RKT, DKVMN",
          "5-Fold Cross-Validation",
          "AST09\n{AUC: 0.842 - KTA_LSTM, F1-Score: 0.841 - KTA & KTA_LSTM}\n\nAST15\n{AUC: 0.829 - KTA_LSTM, F1-Score: 0.843 - KTA_LSTM}\n\nASTChall\n{AUC: 0.757 - KTA_LSTM, F1-Score: 0.557 - KTA_LSTM}\n\nStatics\n{AUC: 0.845 - KTA_LSTM, F1-Score: 0.909 - KTA_LSTM}\n\nSynthetic\n{AUC: 0.826 - KTA, F1-Score: 0.796 - KTA}",
          "Authors propose 2 KT models using Attention mechanisms.\n\nThe model using Attention and LSTMs outperforms the remaining baselines on most datasets except the synthetic one.\n\nThe evaluation is done at 2 levels: First comparison of KTA with other models, which KTA_LSTM outperforms the remaining models.\n\nSecondly, the authors make a comparison of these models against other Attention-Based Models - AKT, SAKT, RKT, DKVMN, which are also outperformed by KTA.\n\nFinally, the authors do an Ablation study to see the effects of hyper-parameter tuning on model performance.",
          "Does not consider behavioral data. "
        ]
      ],
      "index": 5
    }
  ],
